{"tid":102174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醒啦，奉勸各位","createTime":"2017-01-31T12:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T17:54:00.000Z","uid":67789,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9081b68d01eaa300626d4d03d13b3ee23f143f4","tid":102174,"uid":67789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:24:09.000Z","msg":"唔好再比追唔到既愛情浪費時間，比個限期自己追唔到就放手啦。<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀，唔好花咁多時間係打機到，比啲時間去學下其他野進修下啦，做個識得多野有用既人好過日日係屋企打機啦。<br />\n<br />\n拎啲時間陪下屋企人，如果唔係當你屋企人有事果陣你就會後悔架喇，我曾經好憎媽媽煮既飯，但當佢之前大病完，我就知道可以食佢煮既飯係幸福。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲，珍惜你既時間，相信大家都試過好後悔啲時間哂左，但點解你要拎啲時間來浪費同後悔，而唔一早就珍惜呢。<br />\n<br />\n利申：大家可以當我打完丁，聖人Mode，但真心想大家珍惜時間"},{"pid":"3b707e6f9e2825b36007d99f190d558c188933d1","tid":102174,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"唔開心"},{"pid":"30f08672caaf5814f91402e7e45ea202fdc8f77b","tid":102174,"uid":56718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"樓主講得啱 所以我都同自己講左4月前追唔到就由佢啦"},{"pid":"4fe46425ebfb8c139735b167d5890b3827764593","tid":102174,"uid":28647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},{"pid":"25d2c557da05a912ae7ded0c265b3f7a8fdcc589","tid":102174,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"人類總要犯同樣既錯，珍惜時間，老師家人朋友，個個都同自己講過啦"},{"pid":"61f59533ee70c83e5157bbcd779cd90ff56c26bf","tid":102174,"uid":14171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"唉,如果下世都追唔到就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b696195b567344db09f341d061ab83e0a216ef","tid":102174,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"講得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前有次打完丁之後聖人模式覺得冇必要為啲數據咁博命，就戒左打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （個時每日起碼打8個鐘red alert 2"},{"pid":"780f102ad9e3e6805e29371ac3b99799e71fc45c","tid":102174,"uid":67789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"打機真係好浪費時間，係到不停追啲自己拎黎打飛機既LV，牌，裝，都唔知有咩意思。<br />\n<br />\n以前小學初中日日打十幾個鐘，而家諗返起我自己都驚。之後升到上中四娘親大病左一次，我就決定要發奮讀書唔再打機，有時間都拎黎陪下佢。"},{"pid":"aa87944833ddf713743f5d9334d81379827dd5f7","tid":102174,"uid":67789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd412e4812589932ba691c770a2cebf516710fa","tid":102174,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"唔打機仲有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a61576b26748bba05331b415650c095b6c771e","tid":102174,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225f45d113f165454d028724c6bcad98a0010a35","tid":102174,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔打機仲有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下書，落街跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06885de2af6b7af47cd8472473792510bd785882","tid":102174,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔打機仲有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下書，落街跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇書都還可以<br />\n但個人好懶<br />\n又無乜朋友可以約出去<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知打機好哂時間"},{"pid":"09036c15ffa6671d3660f9aab3473f7c1e3d309a","tid":102174,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔打機仲有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下書，落街跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇書都還可以<br />\n但個人好懶<br />\n又無乜朋友可以約出去<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知打機好哂時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發摒下自己有冇其他興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}